 Unit – 1
Installation of C#
 What is C#?

C# is a programming language developed by Microsoft.
It is used to develop Windows apps, web apps, games, and software.

Hindi:
C# ek programming language hai jo Microsoft ne banayi hai.

 Steps to Install C#
 Step 1: Install Visual Studio

Download and install Visual Studio from official Microsoft website.

 Choose:
 .NET Desktop Development
C# Support

 Step 2: Create New Project

Open Visual Studio

Click → Create New Project

Select → Console App (.NET)

Click → Next

Give Project Name

Click → Create

 Step 3: Run the Program

Click  Run button
OR press Ctrl + F5

Unit – 2
Write a Program to Print “Hello World”
C# Program
using System;

class Program
{
    static void Main(string[] args)
    {
        Console.WriteLine("Hello World");
    }
}
 Explanation (Very Important for Viva)

using System; → System library use karta hai

class Program → Class define karta hai

Main() → Program yahin se start hota hai

Console.WriteLine() → Output print karta hai

